TITLE: Russian invasion: What is NATO's Article 5?
SUMMARY: President Biden met with Bucharest 9 leaders to reaffirm commitment to Ukraine and NATO's pledge to defend all its territory detailed under its Article 5 charter.

TITLE: Wagner Group: What to know about Russian mercenary group in Ukraine
SUMMARY: The private military company received renewed attention after chief Yevgeniy Prigozhin claimed the Kremlin ordered an attack on his troops and he started marching towards Moscow.
